parameters: The mansion on the outskirts of town
I couldn't help but follow along again...
What business do you have in such a strange cave?

Is it because of the orders from the sorcerer? Is
there something ahead?

But even so, it would be troublesome if we were to
encounter any danger in a place like this...
By the way... why is Clot here?
Hmm... Ah! No, it's nothing, just that...

I came here to search for mushrooms for dinner,
but I got lost. Ahaha...

Well, it's fine, isn't it? We got what we needed
and I was able to help you too!
Phew, shall we go back to town together?

Ah, from now on... I have to deliver this to the
sorcerer's place...
I see... Well, I guess there's no helping it then.
Oh, um... Don't worry about it!
It's fine if everything goes smoothly...

Whenever I talk about the sorcerer, their
expression seems to darken.
Hmm... I wonder if it's just my imagination.
